name: Rainbow Machine
onomoDesc: うきうき Uki uki Describes someone who is happy and excited. In a buoyant mood.

name: Acapulco Gold
onomoDesc: ざくざく Zaku zaku (1) Describes a large number of metal coins or jewels. (2) Describes the sound of chopping vegetables or the like. Also describes cutting something roughly. (3) Describes the sound of gravel or the like being mixed. (4) Describes the sound of walking over gravel or frost.

name: Avalanch Run
onomoDesc: こつこつ Kotsu kotsu (1) Describes the sound of a large object hitting something, such as shoes hitting the pavement or someone knocking at a door. Tapping. Clicking. Drumming. (2) Describes someone grinding away at their job. Unflaggingly.

name: Arpanoid
onomoDesc: ぎらぎら Gira gira Describes something shining brightly. Dazzlingly. Also used to describe a person's appearance or look. Glaring.

name: Data Corrupter
onomoDesc: きびきび Kibi kibi Describes attitude, behaviour, or speech that is prompt, businesslike, and alert.

name: Disaster Transport Sr
onomoDesc: くたくた Kuta kuta Describes something that is withered. Also is used to describe someone who is realy tired. Worn-out. Exhausted.

name: Dream Crusher
onomoDesc: うじゃうじゃ Uja uja Describes many small things gathered together and moving, such as a swarm of insects or a crowd of people seen from a distance.

name: Hoof Reaper
onomoDesc: かちかち Kachi kachi (1) Describes the sound made when solid objects hit each other. (2) Describes something very hard. Also used to describe someone's stright-laced views or to describe a person who is stiff with nervous tension. Rigid.

name: Hummingbird
onomoDesc: ゆらゆら Yura yura (1) Describes something very loose. (2) Describes slow movement.

name: Levitation
onomoDesc: ぽたぽた Pota pota Describes dripping water.

name: Organizer
onomoDesc: つるつる Tsuru tsuru (1) Describes a smooth surface. Polished. Also describes slipping on a smooth surface. (2) Describes the sound of someone slurping noodles.

name: Palisades
onomoDesc: ぐちゃぐちゃ Gucha gucha (1) Describes something soft and soggy. Also describes the action of stiring or mashing such a substance. (2) Describes something in awful disarray. Higgledy-piigledy. (3) Describes grumbling.

name: Spatial Delivery
onomoDesc: けばけば Keba keba Describes someone or something that is gaudy. Garish.
